	<div id="articleHead">
		<h1>The Non-Expert</h1>

		<h2>Begging the Question</h2>
		<p>Experts answer what they know. The Non-Expert answers anything. This week, <b>ERIC FEEZELL</b> explains the phrase nobody understands in terms we can all understand. For the most part.</p>
	</div>


	<div id="articleRight">
	
	
